name: Cyclone Phil and the Artifact of Southern New Jersey
name_original: Cyclone Phil and the Artifact of Southern New Jersey
description:
(Fullscreen for best experience!)

Join the most renowned treasure hunter in the world - Cyclone Phil - On a daring and funny adventure in southern New Jersey. On the way, there'll be many hidden secrets, fun puzzles, and just all around goofiness.

This has been one of my favorite games to make, so I hope you enjoy it!
